00:04:31.188 --> 00:04:35.224
He said, "And it's not me, 
because I like you people."

00:04:35.224 --> 00:04:36.526
(Laughs)

00:04:36.526 --> 00:04:40.257
And that's what I did, too.
I chuckled, too.

00:04:40.257 --> 00:04:42.233
He said, "But here's the problem:

00:04:42.233 --> 00:04:46.542
If I let you in, the other tenants 
will move out

00:04:46.542 --> 00:04:49.725
and I can't afford to take
that kind of a hit."

00:04:49.725 --> 00:04:52.052
He said, "I just can't rent to you."

00:04:52.052 --> 00:04:54.603
Even though that was discouraging,
it didn't stop me.

00:04:54.603 --> 00:04:55.933
I kept looking,

00:04:55.933 --> 00:05:00.233
